                <li>添加了自动闪避功能, 可以修复多个置顶窗口发生重叠时的激活顺序问题</li>
                <li>添加了新的快捷键, 修复了已知的其他问题</li>
                </ul><ul>
                <li>Supports adjusting the opacity of pinned windows.</li>
                <li>Added "auto-ducking" to fix wrong window order when pinned windows overlap.</li>
                <li>Added new hotkey and fixed other known issues.</li>
                </ul><img src="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/Topit/raw/main/img/donate.png" width="250"/>
