        <item>
            <title>v0.1.2</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 16:06:10 +0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>12</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.3</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <style>ul{margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 7;padding-left: 18;}</style><ul>
                <li>支持直接使用鼠标快速选择待置顶的窗口</li>
                <li>支持暂停置顶 (用于兼容 DRM 播放场景等)</li>
                <li>与窗口进行交互时会暂时停止捕获画面以节省电量</li>
                <li>改进了窗口控制按钮, 添加了更多可配置的快捷键</li>
                </ul><ul>
                <li>You can use your mouse to quickly select a window to pin.</li>
                <li>Supports "Pause", which allows a window to be temporarily unpinned.</li>
                <li>Capture will stop when interacting with the window to save power.</li>
                <li>Improved the window control buttons and added more hotkeys.</li>
                </ul><img src="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/Topit/raw/main/img/donate.png" width="250"/>
            ]]></description>
